.nme.com/news/tv/trailer-netflix-david-beckham-documentary-series-bootgate-3500467">大卫·贝克汉姆 (David Beckham) 的 Netflix 纪录片首部预告片讲述了 Bootgate 丑闻，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
